description:
Jimmy Heath! What an amazing spirit that we have been so fortunate to have since the start of the Bebop era. Living 93 years and instilling the history of jazz into many generations that will carry on the legacy of this wonderful music.

Download here...

https://payhip.com/b/hLFw

Thank you for tuning in! 

always positive, always progressing 

**Click here to support and for some goodies** 
https://www.patreon.com/positivelyprogressing

**Follow here and tag for monthly challenges or just to say hey!**
https://www.instagram.com/chrisgsax/

**Connect on Facebook here**
https://www.facebook.com/Positively-Progressing-333849527159551/

**Check out merch here & grab a tee for yourself!** 
https://teespring.com/stores/positively-progressing
New styles added frequently


Theme music provided by the awesome Jeff Schneider...
https://jeffschneidermusic.com/store
